msgid "Infinispan clusters running in different geographical locations can form global clusters to back up your data across sites. If sites go offline clients can immediately switch to an available cluster, making sure data center faults do not cause service interruptions.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/use-cases/backup-across-data-centers.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "When using the Infinispan Operator with Kubernetes environments such as Red Hat OpenShift,  cross-site replication capabilities make your data ready for hybrid and multi cloud deployments.\n"
msgstr ""

